{"_vrs": {"version": 1, "trace_id": "core-1365", "description": "Negative-path coverage for gateway bearer-token + dcc-scope enforcement on /v1/instances/register. Only meaningful against a gateway started with GatewayAuth populated; against the embedded auto-gateway (GatewayAuth::disabled, the main default), the registration succeeds and this trace is intentionally inactive. The companion Rust integration tests in registration_impl_tests.rs cover the same paths against a unit-style GatewayState so this trace is the live-server complement, not the only coverage."}}
